{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871696722,"sessionID":"ses_285cc90bdffeFYBHSMMEeHfoxo","part":{"id":"prt_d7a3399c00016iptEIYapdZ6CI","messageID":"msg_d7a3388b2001ZgI38gWnPYaz9X","sessionID":"ses_285cc90bdffeFYBHSMMEeHfoxo","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_ff4c249f74dd4ed29acc4cf5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/sandbox-orchestration/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/sandbox-orchestration/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Sandbox Orchestration — Design\n2: \n3: ## Module and dependencies\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|--------|\n7: | Go module | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n8: | Go version (go.mod) | `1.24.4` |\n9: | Toolchain | `go1.24.9` |\n10: \n11: **Direct `require` (from go.mod):**  \n12: `github.com/agiledragon/gomonkey/v2 v2.13.0`, `github.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2 v2.35.0`, `github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.10.0`, `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.2.2`, `github.com/google/uuid v1.6.0`, `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9 v9.17.1`, `github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1`, `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go v1.0.69`, `golang.org/x/net v0.47.0`, `k8s.io/api v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/klog/v2 v2.130.1`, `k8s.io/utils v0.0.0-20251002143259-bc988d571ff4`, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox v0.1.1`, `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2`\n13: \n14: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n15: \n16: ### groupversion_info.go — package and scheme\n17: \n18: ```go\n19: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n20: package v1alpha1\n21: \n22: var (\n23:     GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n24:     SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n25:     AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n26: )\n27: ```\n28: \n29: ### register.go — kind metadata\n30: \n31: ```go\n32: var (\n33:     CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n34:     CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n35:     CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n36:     CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n37: )\n38: \n39: var (\n40:     AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n41:     AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n42:     AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n43: )\n44: \n45: var SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n46: \n47: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n48:     return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n49: }\n50: ```\n51: \n52: ### agent_type.go — AgentRuntime types\n53: \n54: ```go\n55: // +genclient\n56: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n57: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n58: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n59: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n60: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n61: type AgentRuntime struct {\n62:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n63:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n64:     Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n65:     Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n66: }\n67: \n68: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n69:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n70:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n71:     Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n72:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n73:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n74:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n75:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n76:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n77:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n78: }\n79: \n80: type AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n81:     // +optional\n82:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n83: }\n84: \n85: type SandboxTemplate struct {\n86:     // +optional\n87:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,rep,name=labels\"`\n88:     // +optional\n89:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,rep,name=annotations\"`\n90:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n91:     Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=spec\"`\n92: }\n93: \n94: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n95: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n96: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n97:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n98:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n99:     Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n100: }\n101: ```\n102: \n103: ### codeinterpreter_types.go — CodeInterpreter and shared types\n104: \n105: ```go\n106: // +genclient\n107: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n108: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n109: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n110: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n111: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n112: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n113:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n114:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n115:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n116:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n117: }\n118: \n119: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n120:     // +optional\n121:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n122:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n123:     Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n124:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n125:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n126:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n127:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n128:     // +optional\n129:     WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n130:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n131:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n132:     // +optional\n133:     AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n134: }\n135: \n136: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n137:     // +optional\n138:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n139:     // +optional\n140:     Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n141: }\n142: \n143: type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n144:     // +optional\n145:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n146:     // +optional\n147:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n148:     // +optional\n149:     RuntimeClassName *string `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n150:     Image string `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n151:     // +optional\n152:     ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n153:     // +optional\n154:     // +patchMergeKey=name\n155:     // +patchStrategy=merge\n156:     // +listType=map\n157:     // +listMapKey=name\n158:     ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n159:     // +optional\n160:     Environment []corev1.EnvVar `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n161:     // +optional\n162:     // +listType=atomic\n163:     Command []string `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n164:     // +optional\n165:     Args []string `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n166:     // +optional\n167:     Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n168: }\n169: \n170: type TargetPort struct {\n171:     // +optional\n172:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n173:     // +optional\n174:     Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n175:     Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n176:     // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n177:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS;\n178:     Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n179: }\n180: \n181: type AuthModeType string\n182: \n183: const (\n184:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n185:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n186: )\n187: \n188: type ProtocolType string\n189: \n190: const (\n191:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n192:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n193: )\n194: \n195: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n196: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n197: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n198:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n199:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n200:     Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n201: }\n202: ```\n203: \n204: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types`\n205: \n206: ```go\n207: const (\n208:     AgentRuntimeKind    = \"AgentRuntime\"\n209:     CodeInterpreterKind = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n210:     SandboxKind         = \"Sandbox\"\n211:     SandboxClaimsKind   = \"SandboxClaim\"\n212: )\n213: \n214: type SandboxInfo struct {\n215:     Kind             string              `json:\"kind\"`\n216:     SandboxID        string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n217:     SandboxNamespace string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n218:     Name             string              `json:\"name\"`\n219:     EntryPoints      []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n220:     SessionID        string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n221:     CreatedAt        time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n222:     ExpiresAt        time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n223:     Status string `json:\"status\"`\n224: }\n225: \n226: type SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n227:     Path     string `json:\"path\"`\n228:     Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n229:     Endpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"`\n230: }\n231: \n232: type CreateSandboxRequest struct {\n233:     Kind      string `json:\"kind\"`\n234:     Name      string `json:\"name\"`\n235:     Namespace string `json:\"namespace\"`\n236: }\n237: \n238: type CreateSandboxResponse struct {\n239:     SessionID   string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n240:     SandboxID   string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n241:     SandboxName string              `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n242:     EntryPoints []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n243: }\n244: \n245: func (car *CreateSandboxRequest) Validate() error\n246: ```\n247: \n248: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/api`\n249: \n250: ```go\n251: const (\n252:     resourceGroup               = \"agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n253:     sessionResourceName         = \"sessions\"\n254:     agentRuntimeResourceName    = \"agentruntimes\"\n255:     codeInterpreterResourceName = \"codeinterpreters\"\n256: )\n257: \n258: var (\n259:     ErrAgentRuntimeNotFound    = errors.New(\"agent runtime not found\")\n260:     ErrCodeInterpreterNotFound = errors.New(\"code interpreter not found\")\n261:     ErrTemplateMissing         = errors.New(\"resource has no pod template\")\n262:     ErrPublicKeyMissing        = errors.New(\"public key not yet loaded from Router Secret\")\n263: )\n264: \n265: func NewSessionNotFoundError(sessionID string) error\n266: func NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError(namespace, name, kind string) error\n267: func NewUpstreamUnavailableError(err error) error\n268: func NewInternalError(err error) error\n269: ```\n270: \n271: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n272: \n273: ### Config and Server\n274: \n275: ```go\n276: type Config struct {\n277:     Port             string\n278:     RuntimeClassName string\n279:     EnableTLS        bool\n280:     TLSCert          string\n281:     TLSKey           string\n282:     EnableAuth       bool\n283: }\n284: \n285: type Server struct {\n286:     config            *Config\n287:     router            *gin.Engine\n288:     httpServer        *http.Server\n289:     k8sClient         *K8sClient\n290:     sandboxController *SandboxReconciler\n291:     tokenCache        *TokenCache\n292:     informers         *Informers\n293:     storeClient       store.Store\n294:     wg                sync.WaitGroup\n295: }\n296: ```\n297: \n298: ### HTTP routes\n299: \n300: | Method | Path | Auth middleware | Handler |\n301: |--------|------|-----------------|---------|\n302: | GET | `/health` | No | `handleHealth` |\n303: | POST | `/v1/agent-runtime` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleAgentRuntimeCreate` |\n304: | DELETE | `/v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleDeleteSandbox` |\n305: | POST | `/v1/code-interpreter` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleCodeInterpreterCreate` |\n306: | DELETE | `/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleDeleteSandbox` |\n307: \n308: ### ErrorResponse\n309: \n310: ```go\n311: type ErrorResponse struct {\n312:     Message string `json:\"message\"`\n313: }\n314: ```\n315: \n316: ### K8sClient and defaults\n317: \n318: ```go\n319: const (\n320:     DefaultSandboxTTL         = 8 * time.Hour\n321:     DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n322: )\n323: \n324: var (\n325:     SessionIdLabelKey         = \"runtime.agentcube.io/session-id\"\n326:     WorkloadNameLabelKey      = \"runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name\"\n327:     SandboxNameLabelKey       = \"runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name\"\n328:     LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"\n329:     IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey  = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"\n330: )\n331: \n332: type K8sClient struct {\n333:     clientset       *kubernetes.Clientset\n334:     dynamicClient   dynamic.Interface\n335:     scheme          *runtime.Scheme\n336:     baseConfig      *rest.Config\n337:     clientCache     *ClientCache\n338:     dynamicInformer dynamicinformer.DynamicSharedInformerFactory\n339:     informerFactory informers.SharedInformerFactory\n340:     podInformer     cache.SharedIndexInformer\n341:     podLister       listersv1.PodLister\n342: }\n343: ```\n344: \n345: - REST config: `QPS = 50`, `Burst = 100`; in-cluster config else kubeconfig loading rules.\n346: - `NewClientCache(100)` for user dynamic clients.\n347: \n348: ### GVR variables (`informers.go`)\n349: \n350: ```go\n351: var (\n352:     AgentRuntimeGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n353:         Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"agentruntimes\",\n354:     }\n355:     CodeInterpreterGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n356:         Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"codeinterpreters\",\n357:     }\n358:     SandboxGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n359:         Group: \"agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"sandboxes\",\n360:     }\n361:     SandboxClaimGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n362:         Group: \"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"sandboxclaims\",\n363:     }\n364: )\n365: ```\n366: \n367: ### Identity secret (workload_builder.go)\n368: \n369: ```go\n370: const (\n371:     IdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"\n372:     PublicKeyDataKey   = \"public.pem\"\n373: )\n374: \n375: var IdentitySecretNamespace = \"default\" // overridden by env AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE if set\n376: ```\n377: \n378: ### Sandbox reconciler\n379: \n380: ```go\n381: type SandboxReconciler struct {\n382:     client.Client\n383:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n384:     watchers map[types.NamespacedName]chan SandboxStatusUpdate\n385:     mu       sync.RWMutex\n386: }\n387: \n388: type SandboxStatusUpdate struct {\n389:     Sandbox *sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox\n390: }\n391: ```\n392: \n393: - `Reconcile`: when `getSandboxStatus(sandbox) == \"running\"`, notify waiter channel (buffer 1), non-blocking send with `default` branch warning on full channel.\n394: - `getSandboxStatus`: returns `\"running\"` if a condition has `Type == string(sandboxv1alpha1.SandboxConditionReady)` and `Status == metav1.ConditionTrue`, else `\"unknown\"`.\n395: \n396: ### Garbage collector\n397: \n398: ```go\n399: const gcOnceTimeout = 2 * time.Minute\n400: \n401: type garbageCollector struct {\n402:     k8sClient   *K8sClient\n403:     interval    time.Duration\n404:     storeClient store.Store\n405: }\n406: ```\n407: \n408: - `newGarbageCollector(k8s, store, 15*time.Second)` — **GC interval: 15s**.\n409: - Per tick: `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, time.Now().Add(-DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout), 16)` — **batch size 16**.\n410: - `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, time.Now(), 16)` — **batch size 16**.\n411: - Single tick context timeout: **2 minutes**.\n412: \n413: ### Token cache\n414: \n415: - `NewTokenCache(1000, 5*time.Minute)` — max entries **1000**, TTL **5m** per entry (LRU + last-access expiry).\n416: \n417: ### Auth context keys\n418: \n419: ```go\n420: type contextKey string\n421: \n422: const (\n423:     contextKeyUserToken          contextKey = \"userToken\"\n424:     contextKeyServiceAccount     contextKey = \"serviceAccount\"\n425:     contextKeyServiceAccountName contextKey = \"serviceAccountName\"\n426:     contextKeyNamespace          contextKey = \"namespace\"\n427: )\n428: ```\n429: \n430: ### CLI flags (`cmd/workload-manager/main.go`)\n431: \n432: | Flag | Default | Meaning |\n433: |------|---------|---------|\n434: | `-port` | `8080` | API port |\n435: | `-runtime-class-name` | `kuasar-vmm` | Stored on `Config.RuntimeClassName` (flag parsed in `main`; **not read** elsewhere in `pkg/workloadmanager` in current source) |\n436: | `-enable-tls` | `false` | TLS |\n437: | `-tls-cert` | `\"\"` | Cert path |\n438: | `-tls-key` | `\"\"` | Key path |\n439: | `-enable-auth` | `false` | TokenReview auth |\n440: \n441: - Controller-runtime manager: metrics bind `0`, health probe `0`.\n442: - Shutdown: HTTP shutdown timeout **15s**, then cancel ctx, `WaitForBackgroundWorkers`, `CloseStore`.\n443: \n444: ### Store dependency\n445: \n446: ```go\n447: // github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store\n448: type Store interface {\n449:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n450:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n451:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n452:     UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n453:     DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n454:     ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n455:     ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n456:     UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n457:     Close() error\n458: }\n459: ```\n460: \n461: Server uses `store.Storage()` singleton.\n462: \n463: ### Sandbox build notes\n464: \n465: - AgentRuntime: sandbox name `{workloadName}-{RandString(8)}`, UUID session ID, ports from `spec.Ports`, TTL/idle from `MaxSessionDuration` / `SessionTimeout` when non-nil.\n466: - CodeInterpreter: default ports if empty: single `TargetPort{Port:8080, Protocol:ProtocolTypeHTTP, PathPrefix:\"/\"}`; if `WarmPoolSize > 0`: creates `SandboxClaim` + minimal `Sandbox` metadata only, `sandboxEntry.Kind = SandboxClaimsKind`; else builds full `Sandbox` with container `code-interpreter` and optional `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` when `AuthMode == picod`.\n467: - `buildSandboxObject`: APIVersion `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, Kind `Sandbox`, labels include `managed-by: agentcube-workload-manager`, annotation `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey` = idle duration string, lifecycle `ShutdownTime` = now+TTL, `Replicas: ptr.To[int32](1)`.\n468: \n469: ### Pod name annotation\n470: \n471: - Read from created sandbox: key from `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/controllers`.`SandboxPodNameAnnotation` (comment in source documents value `agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name`).\n472: \n473: ## CodeInterpreter controller (supplementary)\n474: \n475: - Reconciles `CodeInterpreter`; when `WarmPoolSize > 0` ensures `SandboxTemplate` (name = CI name) and `SandboxWarmPool` (name = CI name, replicas = WarmPoolSize, templateRef name = CI name); injects `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` in template unless `AuthModeNone`; requeues 5s if public key not cached and auth not none.\n\n(End of file - total 475 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Sandbox Orchestration — Design\n\n## Module and dependencies\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|--------|\n| Go module | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| Go version (go.mod) | `1.24.4` |\n| Toolchain | `go1.24.9` |\n\n**Direct `require` (from go.mod):**  \n`github.com/agiledragon/gomonkey/v2 v2.13.0`, `github.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2 v2.35.0`, `github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.10.0`, `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.2.2`, `github.com/google/uuid v1.6.0`, `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9 v9.17.1`, `github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1`, `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go v1.0.69`, `golang.org/x/net v0.47.0`, `k8s.io/api v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/klog/v2 v2.130.1`, `k8s.io/utils v0.0.0-20251002143259-bc988d571ff4`, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox v0.1.1`, `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2`\n\n## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n\n### groupversion_info.go — package and scheme\n\n```go\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"specs/sandbox-orchestration/design.md","time":{"start":1775871696682,"end":1775871696719}}}}
