{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871727795,"sessionID":"ses_285cc90bdffeFYBHSMMEeHfoxo","part":{"id":"prt_d7a34158d001m27VOGdVgwSLMa","messageID":"msg_d7a33fbc0001hrWRcMvonaYYl1","sessionID":"ses_285cc90bdffeFYBHSMMEeHfoxo","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_fe71f3d76dec461489e59864","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/PLAN.md","limit":200},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/PLAN.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube Implementation Plan — AR-023 through AR-033\n2: \n3: This plan maps Architectural Requirements AR-023 through AR-033 to specific files and implementation details based on the specifications in `./specs/`.\n4: \n5: ## AR Mapping Overview\n6: \n7: | AR | Spec Domain | Package/Path | Description |\n8: |----|-------------|--------------|-------------|\n9: | AR-023 | integrations | `integrations/dify-plugin/` | Dify plugin manifest and provider structure |\n10: | AR-024 | integrations | `integrations/dify-plugin/` | Dify tool schema and implementation |\n11: | AR-025 | example | `example/pcap-analyzer/` | PCAP analyzer FastAPI service |\n12: | AR-026 | deployment | `manifests/charts/base/` | Helm chart templates for Workload Manager |\n13: | AR-027 | deployment | `manifests/charts/base/` | Helm chart templates for Router |\n14: | AR-028 | deployment | `manifests/charts/base/` | Helm chart RBAC and optional Volcano scheduler |\n15: | AR-029 | deployment | `docker/`, `Makefile` | Dockerfiles and build targets |\n16: | AR-030 | ci-cd | `.github/workflows/` | GitHub Actions CI/CD pipelines |\n17: | AR-031 | cli-toolkit | `cmd/cli/agentcube/` | CLI pack/build commands |\n18: | AR-032 | cli-toolkit | `cmd/cli/agentcube/` | CLI publish/invoke/status commands |\n19: | AR-033 | python-sdk | `sdk-python/agentcube/` | SDK clients and exception hierarchy |\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: ## AR-023: Dify Plugin Manifest and Provider Structure\n24: \n25: ### Files to Create\n26: \n27: #### 1. `integrations/dify-plugin/main.py`\n28: **Purpose**: Plugin entrypoint that runs the Dify plugin framework.\n29: \n30: **Logic**:\n31: - Import `dify_plugin.Plugin` and `dify_plugin.DifyPluginEnv`\n32: - Instantiate `Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120))`\n33: - Call `.run()` to start the plugin HTTP server\n34: - Block until the host stops the process\n35: \n36: #### 2. `integrations/dify-plugin/manifest.yaml`\n37: **Purpose**: Root plugin manifest for Dify platform registration.\n38: \n39: **Structure**:\n40: ```yaml\n41: version: 0.0.2\n42: type: plugin\n43: author: volcano-sh\n44: name: agentcube\n45: label:\n46:   en_US: Agentcube\n47:   ja_JP: Agentcube\n48:   zh_Hans: Agentcube\n49:   pt_BR: Agentcube\n50: description:\n51:   en_US: AgentCube integration for Dify\n52:   zh_Hans: AgentCube 集成\n53: icon: icon.png\n54: icon_dark: icon-dark.png\n55: resource:\n56:   memory: 1048576  # 1MB\n57:   permission:\n58:     tool: true\n59:     model: false\n60:     endpoint: false\n61:     app: false\n62:     storage: false\n63: plugins.tools:\n64:   - provider/agentcube.yaml\n65: meta:\n66:   version: 0.0.2\n67:   arch:\n68:     - amd64\n69:     - arm64\n70:   runner:\n71:     language: python\n72:     version: \"3.12\"\n73:     entrypoint: main\n74:   minimum_dify_version: null\n75: created_at: \"2026-03-24T00:00:00Z\"\n76: privacy: null\n77: repo: https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n78: verified: false\n79: ```\n80: \n81: #### 3. `integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.yaml`\n82: **Purpose**: Tool provider descriptor that lists tools and points to Python implementation.\n83: \n84: **Structure**:\n85: ```yaml\n86: identity:\n87:   author: volcano-sh\n88:   name: agentcube\n89:   label:\n90:     en_US: Agentcube Code Interpreter\n91:     zh_Hans: Agentcube 代码解释器\n92:   description:\n93:     en_US: Execute code in AgentCube sandboxes\n94:     zh_Hans: 在 AgentCube 沙箱中执行代码\n95:   icon: icon.png\n96: tools:\n97:   - tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml\n98: extra.python.source: provider/agentcube.py\n99: ```\n100: \n101: #### 4. `integrations/dify-plugin/provider/agentcube.py`\n102: **Purpose**: Python implementation of the Dify tool provider class.\n103: \n104: **Logic**:\n105: - Import `dify_plugin.ToolProvider`\n106: - Import `dify_plugin.errors.tool.ToolProviderCredentialValidationError`\n107: - Define class `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider(ToolProvider)`\n108: - Implement `_validate_credentials(self, credentials: dict[str, Any]) -> None`:\n109:   - Try block: validate that `router_url` and `workload_manager_url` exist in credentials (or implement actual connectivity check)\n110:   - On any exception: raise `ToolProviderCredentialValidationError(str(e))`\n111: - Return without raising on success\n112: \n113: #### 5. `integrations/dify-plugin/requirements.txt`\n114: **Purpose**: Pin Python dependencies for reproducible installs.\n115: \n116: **Content**:\n117: ```\n118: dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0\n119: agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10\n120: ```\n121: \n122: #### 6. `integrations/dify-plugin/.difyignore`\n123: **Purpose**: Specify files to exclude from plugin packaging.\n124: \n125: **Content**:\n126: ```\n127: __pycache__/\n128: *.pyc\n129: .git/\n130: .env\n131: ```\n132: \n133: ---\n134: \n135: ## AR-024: Dify Tool Schema and Implementation\n136: \n137: ### Files to Create\n138: \n139: #### 7. `integrations/dify-plugin/tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml`\n140: **Purpose**: Tool parameter schema for Dify configuration UI.\n141: \n142: **Structure**:\n143: ```yaml\n144: identity:\n145:   name: agentcube-code-interpreter\n146:   author: agentcube\n147:   label:\n148:     human:\n149:       en_US: Code Interpreter\n150:       zh_Hans: 代码解释器\n151:     llm:\n152:       en_US: Execute Python/JavaScript/TypeScript code in a sandbox\n153:   description:\n154:     human:\n155:       en_US: Run code or commands in an AgentCube sandbox\n156:     llm:\n157:       en_US: Use this tool when you need to execute code safely\n158: parameters:\n159:   - name: router_url\n160:     type: string\n161:     required: true\n162:     label:\n163:       en_US: Router URL\n164:     human_description:\n165:       en_US: AgentCube Router endpoint URL\n166:     llm_description: Base URL for the AgentCube Router service\n167:     form: form\n168:   - name: workload_manager_url\n169:     type: string\n170:     required: true\n171:     label:\n172:       en_US: Workload Manager URL\n173:     human_description:\n174:       en_US: AgentCube Workload Manager endpoint URL\n175:     llm_description: Base URL for the Workload Manager control plane\n176:     form: form\n177:   - name: language\n178:     type: select\n179:     required: false\n180:     label:\n181:       en_US: Language\n182:     human_description:\n183:       en_US: Programming language for code execution\n184:     llm_description: One of python, javascript, typescript\n185:     form: llm\n186:     options:\n187:       - value: python\n188:         label:\n189:           en_US: Python\n190:       - value: javascript\n191:         label:\n192:           en_US: JavaScript\n193:       - value: typescript\n194:         label:\n195:           en_US: TypeScript\n196:   - name: code\n197:     type: string\n198:     required: false\n199:     label:\n200:       en_US: Code\n\n(Showing lines 1-200 of 1441. Use offset=201 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube Implementation Plan — AR-023 through AR-033\n\nThis plan maps Architectural Requirements AR-023 through AR-033 to specific files and implementation details based on the specifications in `./specs/`.\n\n## AR Mapping Overview\n\n| AR | Spec Domain | Package/Path | Description |\n|----|-------------|--------------|-------------|\n| AR-023 | integrations | `integrations/dify-plugin/` | Dify plugin manifest and provider structure |\n| AR-024 | integrations | `integrations/dify-plugin/` | Dify tool schema and implementation |\n| AR-025 | example | `example/pcap-analyzer/` | PCAP analyzer FastAPI service |\n| AR-026 | deployment | `manifests/charts/base/` | Helm chart templates for Workload Manager |\n| AR-027 | deployment | `manifests/charts/base/` | Helm chart templates for Router |\n| AR-028 | deployment | `manifests/charts/base/` | Helm chart RBAC and optional Volcano scheduler |\n| AR-029 | deployment | `docker/`, `Makefile` | Dockerfiles and build targets |\n| AR-030 | ci-cd | `.github/workflows/` | GitHub Actions CI/CD pipelines |\n| AR-031 | cli-toolkit | `cmd/cli/agentcube/` | CLI pack/build commands |\n| AR-032 | cli-toolkit | `cmd/cli/agentcube/` | CLI publish/invoke/status commands |\n| AR-033 | python-sdk | `sdk-python/agentcube/` | SDK clients and exception hierarchy |\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"PLAN.md","time":{"start":1775871727761,"end":1775871727793}}}}
